title: Can North Carolina Finish the Job? Or Will the Big Ten Break Through?
description: The Tar Heels are ranked No. 1 after losing last season’s final to Kansas. And Gonzaga figures to be a contender again with Drew Timme among the star big men who’ve returned to college.
dc:creator: Adam Zagoria
media:description: Gonzaga has had N.B.A. talent like Jalen Suggs, Corey Kispert and Chet Holmgren come and go. Drew Timme, right, is still here, and still trying to lead the Zags to their first title.
